Just after dropping his banging latest singles, Mr Eazi has released a vibrant, hard visual to follow up the smash hit, that is gaining massive attention both in the UK Capital and Lagos. “London Town” is his latest single where he features the UK rapper, Giggs, in his upcoming EP ‘Life is Eazi, Vol. 2 – Lagos to London’. To watch the video, click here The song which was produced by Da Beatfreakz provides a hard beat that features a heavyweight verse from Giggs and Mr Eazi switching his style from laid back melodies to hard flows. This switch perfectly echoes the culture shifts from Lagos to London. This is the first release since the Happy Boy signed a label licensing deal with Universal Music Group Africa. Watch out for ‘Life is Eazi, Vol. 2 – Lagos to London’ coming soon!